{"id":385815485,"lang":"cpp","time":"11 months, 1 week","timestamp":1598300697,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"16 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/385815485/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"8.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        std::vector<int> vecLastLoc(256,-1);\n        int nMaxLen = 0 ; \n        int start = 0 ;\n        for (auto i = 0; i < s.size(); i++){\n           if(vecLastLoc[s[i]] >= start) {\n               start = vecLastLoc[s[i]]+1;\n           }\n           nMaxLen = std::max(nMaxLen,i - start + 1);\n            vecLastLoc[s[i]] = i;\n            \n        }\n       return nMaxLen; \n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
